tspan.tspan: The region is mosty occupied by a rugged farming
community and town that serves it, all surrounded by forest.
North: the road leads past a few small towns and to a river
East: the forest gradually gives way to marsh.
South: the road serves a few farms and fades not quite
West: the road leads past very few farms, the forest thickens
before thinning again as the road rises into highlands and
leads to a seldom travelled mountain pass.
